480
00:38:08,370 --> 00:38:11,067
So I'm reliving the past,

481
00:38:11,068 --> 00:38:13,505
repeating a ritual with Marion?

482
00:38:13,528 --> 00:38:15,442
Don't ask me.

483
00:38:15,466 --> 00:38:20,363
I'm just a man hiding in the corner
with my camera, watching.

484
00:38:20,387 --> 00:38:24,575
My camera will tell you the truth.
The absolute truth.

485
00:38:26,324 --> 00:38:28,168
Hitch, I have a question.

